text.section:
This subtitle does not apply to:
a dentist or professional dental corporation that accepts payment on a fee-for-service basis for providing specific dental services to individual patients for whom the services have been prediagnosed;
an authorized insurer whose activities are authorized and regulated under other provisions of this article;
a nonprofit health service plan that is subject to Subtitle 1 of this title;
a health maintenance organization that is authorized by and subject to Title 19, Subtitle 7 of the Health - General Article; or
a dental plan whose regulation by the State is preempted by federal law.
